smaps_pte_range() connected to pmd_entry() does both of pmd loop and pte loop.
So this patch moves pte part into smaps_pte() on pte_entry() as expected by
the name.

ChangeLog v2:
- rebase onto mmots

Signed-off-by: Naoya Horiguchi <n-horiguchi@ah.jp.nec.com>
